OL,3,CDonald Campbell's Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane returns to Coniston Water
OL,6,FDonald Campbell's Bluebird K7 is
OL,7,Freturning to run on Coniston Water for
OL,8,Fthe first time since it crashed there
OL,9,Fin 1967.
OL,11,FThe iconic craft is making its
OL,12,Fcomeback as part of a week-long
OL,13,Ffestival, marking the 70th anniversary
OL,14,Fof its speed record successes on the
OL,15,Flake.
OL,17,FDuring its return to the water the
OL,18,Fhydroplane is expected to hit speeds
OL,19,Fof up to 150mph.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/11
