FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1778595071
OL,3,CDonald Campbell's Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane returns to Coniston Water
OL,6,FFestival events include Donald
OL,7,FCampbell's Land Rover and other
OL,8,Fclassic cars on display, and the visit
OL,9,Fof predecessor Blue Bird K3, the craft
OL,10,Fhis father Sir Malcom Campbell used to
OL,11,Fset world speed records during the
OL,12,Flate 1930s, which should also take to
OL,13,Fthe water, conditions permitting.
OL,15,FA series of evening presentations are
OL,16,Falso planned, including "Full Steam
OL,17,FAhead" presented by Don Wales,
OL,18,FCampbell's nephew, on Thursday 14th
OL,19,FMay, in which attendees can hear the
OL,20,Fstory behind Britain's ambitious steam-
OL,21,Fpowered land-speed record challenge.
OL,26,@xD@YOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
