PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1778595071
OL,3,CDonald Campbell's Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane returns to Coniston Water
OL,6,FJeff Carroll, Chair of Coniston
OL,7,FInstitute & Ruskin Museum, said: "In
OL,8,Fshowing that K7 is fully operational,
OL,9,Fwe hope to inspire a new generation of
OL,10,Fengineers to think big, think bold and
OL,11,Ffor local schoolchildren to remember
OL,12,Fthat a place like Coniston, where they
OL,13,Fcall home, can be the site of
OL,14,Fsignificant world history."
OL,16,FTraffic, parking and visitor
OL,17,Fmanagement plans are in place, with
OL,18,Fcontrolled viewing areas and
OL,19,Frestrictions on waterborne access and
OL,20,Funauthorised drone use.
OL,26,@oD@bOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
