PN,35410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1778595071
OL,3,CDonald Campbell's Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane returns to Coniston Water
OL,6,FTravelling at around 300mph, Bluebird
OL,7,Fleft the surface of the lake,
OL,8,Fsomersaulted and plunged nose-first
OL,9,Finto the water. Campbell was killed
OL,10,Finstantly.
OL,12,FWhen K7 was recovered from the lake in
OL,13,F2001, Donald Campbell's body was also
OL,14,Ffound.
OL,16,FHe was buried in Coniston where both
OL,17,Fhe and his boat now remain.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
